{#{{ include('@IIABMagnet/Report/header.html.twig') }}#}
{{ header | raw }}
<div class="push">
    <p>Guardian of {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }}<br />
        {{ submission.address }}<br />
        {{ submission.city }}, {{ submission.state|upper }} {{ submission.zip }}</p>

    <p>Congratulations! Your application to the Tuscaloosa Public Schools Magnet Program for {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }} for the {{ submission.openEnrollment }} school year has been processed and awarded a conditional* offer for the following two choices:</p>

    <p>1. Your student can be Wait Listed for his/her first choice: {{ waitListedSchools }}. Should additional spaces become available, those spaces will be filled by students on the Wait List based on each studentâ€™s lottery number. If spaces become available and your student is selected for a space based on his/her lottery number, our office will contact you and award your student a space at this school. Please note that the Wait List expires on {{ waitlistExpiresDate|date("Y") }}.</p>

    <p>2. Your student has been accepted for placement at his/her second choice: {{ awardedSchool }}</p>

    <p><strong>You have two choices for accepting or declining one of the options above</strong>:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>You may go online at <strong>{{ acceptanceURL }}</strong> to accept or decline this offer.</li>
        <li>You may mail this letter to the offered school with your choice indicated OR bring this letter to the offered school in person.</li>
    </ul>

    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" style="table-layout:fixed; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td width="40%" style="font-weight:bold;"><strong>Deadline to Accept or Decline:</strong></td>
            <td width="60%" style="font-weight:bold;" align="center"><strong>{{ acceptOnlineDate }}; {{ acceptOnlineTime }} online<br />OR<br />{{ acceptOfflineDate }}; {{ acceptOfflineTime }} by phone</strong></td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>


    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" style="table-layout:fixed; border:1px solid #000000; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td style="font-weight:bold;"><strong>IMPORTANT: If you do not accept or decline online or by phone by {{ acceptOnlineDate }}, your Magnet offer will automatically be DECLINED.</strong></td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>Please note, applicants are awarded only one offer, but may choose to not accept the offer and be waitlisted for another school choice.</p>

    <p><strong>*All offers for 2-12 grade students are conditional upon your student meeting the grade point average and conduct requirements for the offered magnet school.</strong></p>
</div>
